name.trans: Transmitator Ordin de Invazie a brigazii

description.trans:
Un simplu transmitator care poate fi legat de canalul criptat al brigazii tale si poate da un ordin de invazie.
        Acest obiect este necesar pentru a activa Gang Dungeons
description.eng:
A simple transmitter device that can be bind to your gang encrypted channel and give out invasion order.
        This item is required to activate Gang Dungeons

descriptionv2.trans:
Contine articole si resurse gresite pentru ca o brigada sa ramana functionala. 
         Poate fi folosit in sediul central al brigazii
descriptionv2.eng:
Contains misc items and resources for a gang to stay functional.
        Can be used in your gang headquarters

description.trans:
Un fragment de memorie contine secretele criptate ale brigazii, 
        decripteaza aceasta in Cartierul General al brigazii tale pentru a obtine informatii utile (necesita sa fi parte intr-o brigada)
description.eng:
A memory shard contains encrypted gang secrets, 
        decrypt this in your gang headquarters to gain useful intel (requires to be in a gang)

description.trans: Un fragment de memorie vanduta la negru, contine un algoritm si schite foarte criptat(e) care este crucial in procesul de upgradare a echipamentului
description.eng: A black market memory shard contains highly encrypted algorithm and schematic that is crucial in the process of upgrading equipments

description.trans: Contine fragmente de avans AI concepute pentru a ajuta la modernizarea echipamentelor. Cand este utilizat, scade sansa de esec distructiv cu ${percent}% (Stackable) pentru ${duration} minute
description.eng: Contains fragments of advance AI designed to assist with upgrading equipments. When used, decreases the chance of destructive failure by ${percent}% (stackable) for ${duration} minutes

description.trans: Contine fragmente de avans AI concepute pentru a ajuta la modernizarea echipamentelor. Atunci cand sunt utilizate, scade sansa de esec distructiv cu ${percent}% (Stackable pentru ${maxStack} Times) pentru ${duration} minute.Acest efect se va aplica tuturor jucatorilor online
description.eng: Contains fragments of advance AI designed to assist with upgrading equipments. When used, decreases the chance of destructive failure by ${percent}% (stackable for ${maxStack} times) for ${duration} minutes.This effect will apply to all players online

description.trans:
Contine fragmente de avans AI concepute pentru a ajuta la modernizarea echipamentelor. 
         Cand este utilizat, scade sansa de esec distructiv cu 50% timp de 5 minute. acest lucru va afecteaza singurul. 
         poti calibra elementele din sediul dvs. de brigada, trebuie sa va alaturati sau sa incepeti mai intai o brigada.
description.eng:
Contains fragments of advance AI designed to assist with upgrading equipments.
        When used, decreases the chance of destructive failure by 50% for 5 minutes. this only affect yourself.
        You can calibrate items in your Gang Headquarters, you must join or start a gang first.

description.trans:
Nano boti experimentali conceputi pentru a reduce si nega efectele destructive ale unei calibrari experimentate, 
        atunci cand acestia sunt activati, toate calibrarile esuate, nu vor distruge obiectul pentru 5 minute.
description.eng:
Experimental nano machines designed to reduces and negate the destructive effect when failing calibration, 
        when this is activated, all calibration fails will not destroy the item for 5 minutes (Applies to all players)

description.trans:
Un saculet antic, uitat, 
        se observa pe o parte, desenul unei broaste ciudate cu o gura mare si buze rosii,
        semnificatia acestui desen amenintator este necunoscuta, dar este util sa tii cateva lucruri mici in el.
        mareste spatiul de inventar atunci cand este echipata.
description.eng:
A forgotten ancient pouch, 
        there is a weird cartoon frog with big mouth and red lips drawing at the side of it,
        the meaning of the ancient ominous drawing is unknown, but it is handy for keep some small object in it.
        increase inventory space when equipped.

description.trans:
Cool si la moda, Borseta, semnata de o legenda cunoscuta ca 'The Rock' acum decenii in urma.
        mareste spatiul de inventar increase atunci cand este echipata.
description.eng:
Cool and fashionable Fanny Pack, signed by a legend called The Rock himself from decades ago.
        increase inventory space when equipped.

description.trans:
Un rucsac mov 'Exploratorul' asemanator unuia de gradinita, are un ecuson cu numele fostului proprietar "Dora". Arati fabulos atunci cand il porti.
        mareste spatiul de inventar atunci cand este purtat.
description.eng:
An old Kindergarten looking Purple 'Explorer' Backpack, it has a name tag with the previous owner's name "Dora" written on it, you look fabulous wearing it.
        increase inventory space when equipped

description.trans:
O geanta standard pentru birou, are o eticheta alba pe care scrie "Arasaka" pe ea, 
        in timp ce este spatioasa si are compartimente si fante high tech pentru depozitarea documentelor, nu este foarte potrivita pentru transportul armelor.
        mareste spatiul de inventar atunci cand este purtata
description.eng:
An standard issue office case, it has a label with whit print with "Arasaka" on it, 
        while it is specious and has some high tech compartment and slots for document storage, it is not not very suitable for carrying weapons
        increase inventory space when equipped

description.trans:
Un robot folosit de armata proiectat sa-ti care echipamentele si sa te insoteasca in mod autonom,
        Cu cele 6 picioare puternice care imita miscarile paianjenilor si cu o IA avansata la bord, 
        poate sa te urmareasca foarte rapid si in liniste, in timp ce evita sa stea in calea oricarei misiuni pe care le indeplinesti,
description.eng:
An military used bot designed to carry your equipments and follows you autonomously,
        with it's six strong legs that imitates the movement of spiders and a advance onboard AI, 
        it can follow you swiftly and quietly while it avoids get in the way of whatever mission you are performing

description.trans:
Un modul de exploatare care intercepteaza pachetele globale de chat si il modifica, efectuand atacul om-in-mijloc. 
         Transforma tot discursul la chat-ul global la pirat vorbesc. Acest lucru afecteaza toti jucatorii timp de 10 minute
description.eng:
A exploit module that intercepts global chat packages and modifies it, performing Man-In-The-Middle attack.
        Transforms all speech at global chat to Pirate Speak. This effects all players for 10 minutes

description.trans:
Un modul de exploatare care intercepteaza pachetele globale de chat si il modifica, efectuand atacul om-in-mijloc. 
         Transformeaza tot vorbirea la chat-ul global la L33T SP34K. Acest lucru afecteaza toti jucatorii timp de 10 minute
description.eng:
A exploit module that intercepts global chat packages and modifies it, performing Man-In-The-Middle attack.
        Transforms all speech at global chat to l33t Sp34k. This effects all players for 10 minutes

description.trans:
Un expwoit Mouwe care intereseaza pachetele de chat Gwobaw si il modifica, pewfowming om-in-the-middwe. 
          Twansfowms aww discurs la chat-ul gwobaw la uwu vorbesc. Acest efect aww pwayews pweed 10 minute
description.eng:
A expwoit moduwe that intewcepts gwobaw chat packages and modifies it, pewfowming man-in-the-middwe attack.
         twansfowms aww speech at gwobaw chat to uwu speak. This effects aww pwayews fow 10 minutes

description.trans:
Ai o dragoste si vei primi dragoste! Toata lumea primeste o dragoste!. 
         Cand se foloseste, toata lumea se iubeste reciproc 
         Acest lucru efecte pe toti jucatorii de 10 minute
description.eng:
You get some love, and you get some love! everyone gets some love!.
        When used everyone loves each other
        This effects all players fow 10 minutes

description.trans: Un Shard stocheaza setarile implicite si algoritmul pentru echipamente, acesta este utilizat pentru resetarea fabricatiilor dvs.
description.eng: A shard stores default settings and algorithm for equipments, this is used for factory-resetting your equipments

description.trans:
Cand este folosit, sariti la 60 de minute pe sarcini AFK. 
         trebuie sa fie utilizat la ecranul AFK
description.eng:
When used, skip 60 minutes on AFK tasks.
        must be used at AFK screen

description.trans:
ingrijorat fratele mare, spionandu-va in timp ce navigati pe spatiul cibernetic? 
         Interfonii dvs. sunt intotdeauna hacked de atacuri rau intentionate? 
         Utilizati Cybertunnel VPN pentru a proteja si cripta experienta dvs. neferning! 
        
         Odata activat, ignora orice chat exploateaza timp de 1 ora
description.eng:
Worried the Big Brother spying on you while you browse the cyberspace?
        your intercoms always get hacked by malicious attacks? 
        use CyberTunnel VPN to protect and encrypt your netrunning experience! 
        
        Once activated, ignores any chat exploit for 1 hour

description.trans:
Un sarpe care contine exploatari in avans. 
         Pot fi folosite pentru a incalca sisteme, cum ar fi cetatea de date Shangri-la
description.eng:
A shard that contains advance exploits. 
        Can be used to breach systems such as Shangri-la Data Fortress

description.trans: Un container criptat cu decor rosu, verde si o sigla "Cybersstanta " pe partea ei.
description.eng: An encrypted container with red, green decoration and a 'CyberSanta' logo on the side of it.

descriptionv3.trans: Un sarpe care contine exploatari in avans concepute pentru a creste sansele de scadere aleatorie a articolelor de nivel inalt. Castiga sanse de scadere a legendarului (${legendaryChance}%) si Epic (${epicChance}%) la deblocarea containerelor legendare (nu sunt stivuite) pentru ${time} Minut. * Important: Bufful se va aplica numai cand procesul de deblocare este pornit in timp ce bufful este activ *.
descriptionv3.eng: A shard that contains advance exploits designed to increase random drop chance of high tier items. Gains additional drop chance of Legendary (${legendaryChance}%) and Epic (${epicChance}%) items when unlocking Legendary containers (Not stackable) for ${time} minute (Applies to all players). *IMPORTANT: The buff will only apply when the unlocking process is started while the buff is active*.

description.trans: O grenada flash care poate fi folosita pentru Inamici orbi. Cresterea sansei de a scapa de ${escape}%
description.eng: A flash grenade that can be used to blind enemies. increasing your chance of escape by ${escape}%

description.trans: Un dovleac sculptat care este aprins de un LED in interior. Este un articol decorativ pentru Halloween.
description.eng: A carved pumpkin that is lit by a LED inside. It's a decorative item use for of Halloween. You can craft a Locked Legendary Container with 100 of this

description.trans: in timp ce Shard este activ, toti jucatorii pot alege sa inceapa anumite sarcini AFK in Boost Mode , obtinand ${rewardMult} X recompensa in timp ce creste costurile si durata cu ${costMult} x. \ n * Acest articol este inca beta si este supus schimbarii echilibrului, va rugam sa utilizati imediat dupa cumparare *
description.eng: While shard is active all players can choose to start certain AFK tasks in Boost Mode, gaining ${rewardMult}x reward while increasing cost and duration by ${costMult}x. \n* This item is still beta and subject to balance change, please use immediately after purchase *

description.trans: Un plic rosu cu un sigiliu digital auriu pe el. Se pare ca contine un fel de moneda
description.eng: A red envelope with a golden digital seal on it. looks like it contains some sort of currency

description.trans: O moneda de aur cu o gravura a unui dragon pe ea. Moneda fizica este foarte rara de vazut in aceste zile, ar trebui sa poata cumpara ceva bun cu acesta in districtul pietei
description.eng: A golden coin with a engraving of a dragon on it. physical currency is very rare to see these days, should be able to buy something good with it in the market district

description.trans: Aceste galuste sunt spre deosebire de oricare alta. Realizate cu dragoste si grija de Yen, aceste buzunare delicioase de bunatate sunt umplute cu cele mai bune ingrediente si gatite la perfectiune. \ N recupereaza ${percent}% sanatate la consum
description.eng: These dumplings are unlike any other. Made with love and care by Yen, these delicious pockets of goodness are filled with the finest ingredients and cooked to perfection.\n recover ${percent}% health upon consumption

description.trans: Tortul de orez lipicios si dulce este o mancare traditionala de Anul Nou Lunar si se crede ca aduce noroc si prosperitate. \ N recupereaza ${percent}% scut la consum
description.eng: sticky and sweet rice cake is a traditional Lunar New Year food and is believed to bring good luck and prosperity.\n recover ${percent}% shield upon consumption

description.trans: Facut cu dragoste si grija de Yen. O masa delicioasa si hranitoare care va acorda jucatorului -${percent}% daune suferite timp de 20 de minute cand este mancat. Perfect pentru a face fata provocarilor dure si a cuceri Inamici dificili, sushi -ul lui Yen \ este o necesitate pentru orice aventurier.
description.eng: Made with love and care by Yen. delicious and nourishing meal that will grant the player -${percent}% damage taken for 20 minutes when eaten. Perfect for tackling tough challenges and conquering difficult foes, Yen\'s sushi is a must - have for any adventurer.

description.trans: Un fragment care inglobeaza memoria si experienta cuiva. Daca este activat, poti dobandii ${levelName} experienta din aceast device.
description.eng: A shard that contains someone's memory and experience. If used you may gain ${levelName} experience from this

description.trans:
Fragment de Cheie Secreta folosit pentru a forta-brutal o cheie secreta.
                                Foloseste Terminalul din Centrul Orasului [Hub] pentru a forta-brutal o ${segmentDisplayName} cheie secreta.
                                Poti obtine fiecare din cele 3 fragmente de chei din fiecare dungeon (in cea normala si in cea dificila),
                                arunci cand ai obtinut 3 fragmente de cheie, poti utiliza Terminalul pentru a forta-brutal (crea) o cheie pentru urmatoarea zona.
description.eng:
A secret key Fragment used to brute-force a secret key.
                                Use the Terminal at city center [Hub] to brute-force a ${segmentDisplayName} secret key.
                                You can acquire each of the 3 required keys in each dungeon (both normal or challenge),
                                when you acquired 3 keys, you may use Terminal to brute-force (Craft) a key to the next area

description.trans:
Un ${typeName} cache contine informatii utilizate pentru Printarea Moleculara 3D. 
                    Poti crea un(o) ${typeName} cu [Printerul 3D Molecular] la [Hub-ul Central].
                    
                    Pro tip: Nivelul obiectului pe care il obtii din printare este determinat de nivelul de Printare,
                    asadar, printeaza intotdeauna cele de tip gunoi primele, deoarece au un cost mai redus de printare si sunt folositoare pentru a-ti imbunatatii nivelul de Printare.
description.eng:
A ${typeName} cache contains information used for Molecular 3D Printing, 
                    You can create a ${typeName} with the [Molecular 3d Printer] at [Central Hub].
                    
                    Pro tip: The level of item you get from printing is determined by your Printing Rank,
                    so always print the trash ones first, as they cost less and useful to level up your Printing Rank

description.trans:
[Hub Central]
        Unul din cele mai aglomerate orase de pe continent, aici poti gasii tot felul de oameni din intreaga lume.
description.eng:
[Central Hub]
        One of the busiest cities in the continent. Here you can find all sorts of people from around the globe.

        Poate ca tu o sa gasesti ceva care iti trebuie sau poate ca vrei sa-ti deschizi propriul magazin.
description.eng:

        Folosind tehnologia hyperloop poti calatorii la viteze foarte mari pe intreg continentul cu usurinta.

[Adventure]

description.eng:
